{"tid":1512800,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯卡提名最佳紀錄片以及導演Evgeny Afineevsky 寫給香港人的一封信","createTime":"2019-08-28T04:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:33:21.000Z","uid":153051,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9551b1c1a6f471b2c1cc1e620820d2e0e878d59b","tid":1512800,"uid":153051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"Winter On Fire《凜冬烈火：烏克蘭為自由而戰》<br />\n<br />\n2013年11月21日烏克蘭民眾走上獨立廣場集會抗議，事件演變成血腥衝突，直至2014年2月22日總統亞努科維奇下台，別爾庫特特種部隊永久解散，為其93天抗爭中，示威鎮暴造成至少 125 人死亡，65 人失蹤，1,890 多人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「Freedom isn&rsquo;t free」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n導演Evgeny Afineevsky：<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Remember it&rsquo;s now or never ! With you in spirit ! （切記時不再來，機不可失！我的精神與你們同在！）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1392557894302365/posts/2361382580753220?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1392557894302365%2Fposts%2F2361382580753220%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=9ccb56cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1392557894302365/posts/2361382580753220?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"f14779a3d830beb4a5d7f4a536bc071a294766c6","tid":1512800,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T04:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=9dbfe9b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2F